WEBVTT


00:00:00.220 --> 00:00:02.520
The rich don't tell people what they know.

00:00:03.020 --> 00:00:06.920
One of my best friends just sold his business for $2 billion.

00:00:07.540 --> 00:00:09.260
He and I started at Xerox together,

00:00:09.261 --> 00:00:10.161
by the way.

00:00:10.820 --> 00:00:14.120
And I asked him to come and speak at my company. He says no,

00:00:15.540 --> 00:00:18.160
they don't want to tell people what they do.

00:00:19.060 --> 00:00:22.760
So there is a rich dad. When I asked him if he would help me, he says no.

00:00:24.020 --> 00:00:25.780
So that's, that's what really happened.

00:00:25.781 --> 00:00:28.381
And so I wrote Rich Dad, poor Dad.

00:00:28.382 --> 00:00:31.481
And then Oprah called. Then Trump called.

00:00:31.940 --> 00:00:34.860
And I don't know if you know if Trump is a real guy or not,

00:00:34.861 --> 00:00:36.705
but he's pretty, he's pretty real.
